data.description: Quiet well established neighborhood! Great home with 4 bedrooms/2 bath, 2 car garage, great size front rear yard. Enjoy Solar, low maintenance turf, near schools, shops and  freeways. Extra room off the family room can be used as a future ADU with its own entrance Nice open floor plan,newer laminate floors, separate family room, open concept kitchen! Room for RV and boats. Come check out this move in ready home.
